{"tid":1767363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北約秘書長：中國國際力量日漸提升 但無意視中國為敵人","createTime":"2019-12-03T09:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T11:54:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f193fa4f0b535fdb35ccc627bddf20eecaa7fe0","tid":1767363,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"北約秘書長斯托爾騰貝格(Jens Stoltenberg)表示，中國國際力量日漸提升，北約組織須加以應對，但無意視中國為敵人。<br />\n<br />\n斯托爾騰貝格周一在英國倫敦向CNBC稱，中國的經濟和軍事力量不斷崛起，正在改變全球勢力平衡，同時也帶來一些機會與嚴重挑戰。不過，由29個成員國組成的北約，無意將中國當作敵人。<br />\n<br />\n斯托爾騰貝格又說，中國大力增加基建投資，在經濟和軍事上正逐步逼近歐洲，但北約無意介入某些區域事務，包括南海。因此，這種局面將帶來某些後果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2319245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2319245%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=39fd019c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2319245/</a>"},{"pid":"380bae73fc61597e5e93c16efbae4ca06fb2b371","tid":1767363,"uid":165683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"Fuck You"},{"pid":"c4508feef965a6ad51003a659aae0b460811f8b3","tid":1767363,"uid":269125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"其實好正常，唔通當面話「我地係敵人」咁咩<br />\n會特登出嚟講話要「加以應對」<br />\n其實已經暗示緊冷戰時期美蘇時期既軍事Ｘ科技競賽再臨<br />\n預言定，之後北約軍費應該加得快過通脹"},{"pid":"c19aee1a95493e44bf91356e26be063748d24144","tid":1767363,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cccea7dcc24718e34830c42c4614bf900f399f","tid":1767363,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">北約無意介入某些區域事務，包括南海 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9241501d9a362851276d8be581f574ffb1ea0607","tid":1767363,"uid":276548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"美國退出吧 到時歐豬咪似1,2戰咁要人幫"},{"pid":"f65f4372dd3c61315371da773ec7d8f2e6418240","tid":1767363,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"仲有馬克龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f794d7b7bd4801b8197b13f77a67660470d20cc4","tid":1767363,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65f4372dd3c61315371da773ec7d8f2e6418240","tid":1767363,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"仲有馬克龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普上任以來一直指摘歐洲依賴美國保費，又不願承擔更多軍費。馬克龍批評，北約缺乏內部協調，而美國領導靠不住。他上月底與北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格（Jens Stoltenberg）在巴黎會面時，向傳媒反問：<br />\n<br />\n我們今天的敵人是俄羅斯嗎？是中國嗎？他們是北約的指定敵人嗎？我不這麼認為。聯盟的共同敵人應是恐怖主義，因為它襲擊過我們所有的國家。  <br />\n（Is our enemy today, as I hear sometimes, Russia？ Is it China？ Is it the Atlantic alliance's purpose to designate them as enemies？ I don't think so. Our common enemy at the alliance is, it seems, terrorism, which has hit all of our countries.）<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2511584/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2511584%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a16a6287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2511584/</a>"},{"pid":"29f021ab469f9db392df296d5f87c678cbf0b73b","tid":1767363,"uid":237962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4508feef965a6ad51003a659aae0b460811f8b3","tid":1767363,"uid":269125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"其實好正常，唔通當面話「我地係敵人」咁咩<br />\n會特登出嚟講話要「加以應對」<br />\n其實已經暗示緊冷戰時期美蘇時期既軍事Ｘ科技競賽再臨<br 